divs: Sighting Details "Swords: Life on the Line" episode 'Making Waves' (Discovery Channel). At the approx 40 min mark, there is a shot of the ocean, and in the background a light is moving slowly, and then picking up speed and disappearing. Date and location are unknown to me, however I believe that they were off the Grand Banks, east of main. Middle of the ocean essentially.
Summary: "Swords: Life on the Line" episode 'Making Waves' - 40 min mark
